tps://github.com/wxWidgets/Phoenix/">wxPython's GitHub Repository</a></li><=
/ul> <h2 id=3D"pygobject-gtk">PyGObject (GTK+)</h2> <p><em><strong>Best for=
</strong> developing applications for the GNOME desktop environment.</em></=
p> <p>If you intend to create an application that integrates well with <em>=
